      <p>Students will be housed in <strong>Chouinard Hall</strong> at CalArts. Dorm rooms are double-occupancy, and gender-inclusive housing is available upon request. Trained CSSSA staff and Resident Assistants will be present 24/7 to supervise and support students.</p>
      <p>All rooms include basic furniture, air conditioning, and Wi-Fi. Bathrooms are shared per floor. Students will receive dorm assignments upon arrival.</p>
