      <h2>‚ùìProgram FAQs</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Is the program free?</strong> Yes! There is no tuition. Students only cover transportation and food costs.</li>
        <li><strong>Are meals provided?</strong> Meals are not included, but the CalArts campus has dining options and grocery stores nearby.</li>
        <li><strong>Who can attend?</strong> Students entering grades 9‚Äì12 in Fall 2025, or graduating in Spring 2025.</li>
        <li><strong>Do I need to bring painting materials?</strong> All studio materials (including acrylic paints) will be provided, but you may bring your own sketchbook or tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Can I contact staff if I have more questions?</strong> Yes, please email <a href="mailto:csssa.admissions@gmail.com">csssa.admissions@gmail.com</a>.</li>
